enum affx::tsv_return_t

Return values to signal Error codes.

Enumerator:
TSV_OK  No Error.
TSV_LINE_BLANK  The line is blank (m_lineLvl).
TSV_LINE_COMMENT  The line is a comment line (m_lineLvl).
TSV_ERR_UNKNOWN  An otherwise unknown error.
TSV_ERR_NOTFOUND  The value was not found.
TSV_ERR_NULL  The value was null.
TSV_ERR_CONVERSION  The value could not be converted.
TSV_ERR_FILEIO  Some sort of file IO error.
TSV_ERR_FORMAT  The format of the file is bad.
TSV_ERR_EOF  Hit the end of the file.
TSV_HEADER  A header line was read.
TSV_HEADER_LAST  Did not read a header line.
TSV_LEVEL_LAST  Did not read a line of the correct level.
TSV_FIND_LAST  Found the last matching value.
TSV_LASTVALUE  end of errors
